<h2>Im Reich der Magna Mater (Dissertation)</h2>
<h3>Natália Correia und die Geschichte der Frauen in Portugal</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1321'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
